OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOutbreaks of rain will clear
OL,6,Faway northeast through the morning.
OL,7,FThen turning brighter with scattered
OL,8,Fshowers, occasionally heavy in the
OL,9,Fwest later. Fresh to strong
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA rather cloudy night with
OL,13,Fshowers, heavy at times and merging
OL,14,Finto longer periods of rain near the
OL,15,Fwest coast. Fresh southwest winds,
OL,16,Foccasionally strong around coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
