OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,6,Fscattered showers. Turning brighter
OL,7,Fthrough the afternoon with some
OL,8,Fsunnier spells developing and showers
OL,9,Fbecoming fewer. Brisk winds,
OL,10,Foccasionally strong on the west coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FPatchy
OL,13,Fcloud developing on Sunday alongside
OL,14,Frisk of showers later. A few showers
OL,15,Fon Monday but mostly dry by Tuesday.
OL,16,FWinds lighter than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
